description: Demolition of existing building and erection of a car-free, part 3-, 4-, 5-, 6-, 7- and 8-storey building containing a broadcast studio on part of the ground floor and 5 studio units, 37 one-bedroom flats, 37 two-bedroom flats and 4 three-bedroom flats with basement parking for 29 cars with access off Atlip Road and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 31/03/2006 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended)
